{"tid":288684,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[銀彈炸港超] 港腳羅拔圖收中超人工加盟R&F富力 東方: 正商討轉會費","createTime":"2017-06-18T11:17:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-23T03:36:51.000Z","uid":9030,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e5244bb1f1bfd909973164e3c9c93ec183ca8d2c","tid":288684,"uid":9030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T11:17:26.000Z","msg":"東方總監梁守志接受訪問時確定，攻守大將基奧雲尼及羅拔圖來季將會轉投R&amp;F富力，其中港腳羅拔圖更是以15萬月薪簽約兩年。<br />\n<br />\n尚有一年合約的34歲老將羅拔圖則收到月薪15萬港元、即兩年進帳360萬的合同，梁守志便說：「他們年紀都已經30多歲，很可能是最後一次爭取大合同，無謂強留對方。」<br />\n<br />\n梁守志指羅拔圖離隊雖然已成定局，目前正和富力商討轉會費，相信很快會有結果。"},{"pid":"e5c6dad4ba63a7dae4b0b124f98c3ebf6e29ece2","tid":288684,"uid":35910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T11:54:05.000Z","msg":"邊度值<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c19b0fc7095a3899b71332777121572f045103dc","tid":288684,"uid":9030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T12:36:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>邊度值<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n羅拔圖收到R&amp;F富力兩年月薪15萬元的報價<br />\n基奧雲尼獲R&amp;F富力開價六位數月薪<br />\n周綽豐收到R&amp;F富力近5萬元月薪的報價"},{"pid":"18138c5e4c0585c0b2687bb1012216341636c98c","tid":288684,"uid":15647,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T14:34:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>邊度值<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n本地身份，外援級數，定海神針，合理"},{"pid":"878db778c1816c0c32c3b00b0ace934a7f1b4abf","tid":288684,"uid":37493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T15:00:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>邊度值<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n羅拔圖收到R&amp;F富力兩年月薪15萬元的報價<br />\n基奧雲尼獲R&amp;F富力開價六位數月薪<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">周綽豐收到R&amp;F富力近5萬元月薪的報價</span></blockquote>"},{"pid":"40aa8e5035a18139cd7c1ef598b3a8f70c17d06e","tid":288684,"uid":37493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"re